      "description": "Presenting an exceptional example of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved with the utmost care, it offers an uncompromising experience for the discerning owner. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the impeccable interior appointments, reflects a standard of quality rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This superlative specimen stands as a testament to peak mechanical and aesthetic integrity, representing a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such distinguished caliber.",
      "price": 46800.0,
