    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
