    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This is an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering its 333hp with surgical precision through six individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, the rod bearings addressed, and the rear subframe reinforced for structural longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock that remains tight and responsive. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping and bushing integrity, ensuring a neutral, high-limit handling profile. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a perfect compression profile, this is a turnkey example for the most demanding purist.",
